<item>
            <title>[CXF-2921] PolicyBasedWSS4JInInterceptor not asserting TransportBinding assertion when no message layer security is added</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-2921</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a TransportBinding assertion is used and no message layer security is employed, the WSS4JInInterceptor does not delegate result processing to PolicyBasedWSS4JInInterceptor.  As a result, the transport bindings are not asserted.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
